attributes.title: EXTREME NURSERY RHYMES - Guts and Glory
attributes.caption: Michael and Gavin return to Guts and Glory for a bloody good time.
attributes.description:
Michael and Gavin return to Guts and Glory for a bloody good time.

Jack and Jill went up the hill,
dodging arrows with great skill.
Jack got hit, Jill was split,
but in the end, they would not quit.

Oncoming cars, led to scars,
and bloody streaks along the tar.
Then there's the truck.
Gavin's a scmuck.
And I don't want to rhyme anymore.
